{"tid":1158603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本新興「出租媽媽」月費700元起　上門湊仔做家務陪聊天v","createTime":"2019-05-17T05:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T16:00:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":214,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":115,"replies":[{"pid":"211a70a944507357c9e09815267ae279e0dbcf05","tid":1158603,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"如果媽媽過身，或住所相隔好遠，一定會很掛念媽媽&hellip;&hellip;日本最近有個新服務可讓人一解思親之愁。有公司推出「出租媽媽」服務，最低只需9800日元（約700港元），就可租用媽媽到府上煮飯湊仔做家務，「媽媽」還會用親人口吻方式聊天，令人感到相當溫暖。<br />\n《全日本新聞網》近日追蹤了一位「出租媽媽」的生活，69歲黑田俊美去到一位獨居的年輕女子府上，立即媽媽上身關心「女兒」的近況，以媽媽口吻不斷聊天，並走入廚房為她做沙律、炒菜等料理，還記熟了廚具和日用品的位置，用起來就如自己屋企一樣。<br />\n之後「出租媽媽」到另一個家庭，就像媽媽幫女兒湊小孩，打掃洗衫做家務，她更掌握小朋友的口味烹調食物。<br />\n&quot;出租媽媽︰「這是番薯和吞拿魚沙律，小朋友最喜歡了。」<br />\n客人︰「很好吃，和之前的一樣好吃！」&quot;<br />\n「出租媽媽」黑田俊美是一間名為「東京媽媽」公司旗下員工，本身都是資深家庭主婦，煮飯、做家務、湊小孩通通難不到她。與鐘點工人不同的是，她會讓客人有如家人般的親切感，真的像媽媽照顧孩子一樣。<br />\n根據「東京媽媽」的網頁顯示，最平每月9800日元（約700港元），包3次上門，每次相處6小時內，每延長1小時加收2000日元（約143港元）。<br />\n該公司更推出獨居與夫妻套餐，前者每月17800日元（約1274港元）包5次上門，每次12小時內；後者月費34800日元（約2490港元）包8次上門，可以相處足足24小時，湊初生BB幫手餵夜奶相當划算。<br />\n對新手媽媽來說，花2490元請個「新奶奶」，可能比自己的奶奶更幫得手，又不用受氣！<br />\n「東京媽媽」專門聘用中老年婦女，社長表示，每個「出租媽媽」都很受歡迎，幾乎沒有人被拒絕過；工作亦令退休主婦增加與年輕人的互動機會，達致雙贏。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2350000/2352350/japanmama_thumb_20190517_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2350000%2F2352350%2Fjapanmama_thumb_20190517_ch_1024.jpg&h=fe69cc27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2350000/2352350/rent_mom_01_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2350000%2F2352350%2Frent_mom_01_1024.png&h=7740c1c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n97W5YUuaTk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn97W5YUuaTk&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=7739de83\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n97W5YUuaTk</a>"},{"pid":"e1237d5c808c1a2f631698978e359a26b19d4395","tid":1158603,"uid":100347,"like":538,"dislike":4,"score":534,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:41:01.000Z","msg":"等睇痴線留言"},{"pid":"0755fbf6ff26072455cd941f128daa67010bd15d","tid":1158603,"uid":156511,"like":380,"dislike":7,"score":373,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"地方的媽媽"},{"pid":"df6e15769a589557a2f3f311265b1e8aa25f2798","tid":1158603,"uid":38904,"like":126,"dislike":3,"score":123,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:41:17.000Z","msg":"ptm<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9813503f1b9bc5af4b42d28a55f6076625fc0db5","tid":1158603,"uid":53498,"like":61,"dislike":1,"score":60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:41:43.000Z","msg":"保姆同鐘點"},{"pid":"ea13135a3c81031099ca0bd57ee193e6cd949531","tid":1158603,"uid":15758,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"次數越多越貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063d02495554036044cb14b2d67aa080788ab4d5","tid":1158603,"uid":87620,"like":53,"dislike":16,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:42:29.000Z","msg":"MILF<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80cd1079b13ba720125008c0a7eec89175ca5b43","tid":1158603,"uid":20867,"like":75,"dislike":3,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:45:23.000Z","msg":"世界奇妙物語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4068172f4d2e46cfccf4e8c7d0703efb7d28c85","tid":1158603,"uid":27978,"like":8,"dislike":42,"score":-34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:46:12.000Z","msg":"包唔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fac46affe438b2d4f813efa5cfac67cf0cbaae1","tid":1158603,"uid":98692,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05: