5739,"like":111,"dislike":4,"score":107,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T06:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thy91hN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fthy91hN.gif&h=2d06d464&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0682539ac39f76f042d61a97d180271856d454","tid":1158603,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"211a70a944507357c9e09815267ae279e0dbcf05","tid":1158603,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"如果媽媽過身，或住所相隔好遠，一定會很掛念媽媽&hellip;&hellip;日本最近有個新服務可讓人一解思親之愁。有公司推出「出租媽媽」服務，最低只需9800日元（約700港元），就可租用媽媽到府上煮飯湊仔做家務，「媽媽」還會用親人口吻方式聊天，令人感到相當溫暖。<br />\n《全日本新聞網》近日追蹤了一位「出租媽媽」的生活，69歲黑田俊美去到一位獨居的年輕女子府上，立即媽媽上身關心「女兒」的近況，以媽媽口吻不斷聊天，並走入廚房為她做沙律、炒菜等料理，還記熟了廚具和日用品的位置，用起來就如自己屋企一樣。<br />\n之後「出租媽媽」到另一個家庭，就像媽媽幫女兒湊小孩，打掃洗衫做家務，她更掌握小朋友的口味烹調食物。<br />\n&quot;出租媽媽︰「這是番薯和吞拿魚沙律，小朋友最喜歡了。」<br />\n客人︰「很好吃，和之前的一樣好吃！」&quot;<br />\n「出租媽媽」黑田俊美是一間名為「東京媽媽」公司旗下員工，本身都是資深家庭主婦，煮飯、做家務、湊小孩通通難不到她。與鐘點工人不同的是，她會讓客人有如家人般的親切感，真的像媽媽照顧孩子一樣。<br />\n根據「東京媽媽」的網頁顯示，最平每月9800日元（約700港元），包3次上門，每次相處6小時內，每延長1小時加收2000日元（約143港元）。<br />\n該公司更推出獨居與夫妻套餐，前者每月17800日元（約1274港元）包5次上門，每次12小時內；後者月費34800日元（約2490港元）包8次上門，可以相處足足24小時，湊初生BB幫手餵夜奶相當划算。<br />\n對新手媽媽來說，花2490元請個「新奶奶」，可能比自己的奶奶更幫得手，又不用受氣！<br />\n「東京媽媽」專門聘用中老年婦女，社長表示，每個「出租媽媽」都很受歡迎，幾乎沒有人被拒絕過；工作亦令退休主婦增加與年輕人的互動機會，達致雙贏。<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2350000/2352350/japanmama_thumb_20190517_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2350000%2F2352350%2Fjapanmama_thumb_20190517_ch_1024.jpg&h=fe69cc27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2350000/2352350/rent_mom_01_1024.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2350000%2F2352350%2Frent_mom_01_1024.png&h=7740c1c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n97W5YUuaTk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn97W5YUuaTk&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=7739de83\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n97W5YUuaTk</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:49:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.xvideos.com/video41260937/asian_twinks_gay_hole_ram\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.xvideos.com%2Fvideo41260937%2Fasian_twinks_gay_hole_ram&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=ce7197ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.xvideos.com/video41260937/asian_twinks_gay_hole_ram</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934b6c1dfd033b983e9fb56c869987e6a6d3e69d","tid":1158603,"uid":194281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25801b939ae42891940487ea76ca739756f85004","tid":1158603,"uid":57898,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"雖然大家既留言都好搞笑<br />\n不過我望住篇文忍唔住眼濕濕......<br />\n我媽一年前因為cancer走左<br />\n好想放工返去 佢就出現返<br />\n同我講：衰仔 咁夜返作死你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:52:06.000Z","msg":"連登多中學生<br />\n邊明對你最好既至親<br />\n唔再係人世個心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a3c14724255e8b7022e8227c30a06a2fe5bae8","tid":1158603,"uid":55874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:06:27.000Z","msg":"40路正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88e72ef2f5a747d7f60a6ca15d8d166d54b5ee8","tid":1158603,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:43:16.000Z","msg":"ptm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只限20-30<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"